hian\", \"score\": 0.9086259576533738, \"rank\": 0.10040282601212396, \"text\": \"Kim\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kim_Kardashian\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a terse, four-sentence report\", \"from\": 783, \"to\": 812}, {\"ngram\": \"the quarter-finals\", \"from\": 907, \"to\": 925}, {\"ngram\": \"semi\", \"from\": 930, \"to\": 934}, {\"ngram\": \"finals\", \"from\": 935, \"to\": 941}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The report then detailed how the pair came up short against the world number one duo, China's Wang Chuqin and Sun Yingsha, in the mixed doubles final, losing 4-2 on Tuesday.\", \"from\": 944, \"to\": 1117, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1030, \"end\": 1035, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7848125565451195, \"rank\": 0.2720247247079698, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1038, \"end\": 1049, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wang_Chuqin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Wang Chuqin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13382519\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wang_Chuqin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wang_Chuqin\"}, {\"begin\": 1054, \"end\": 1065, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sun_Yingsha\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sun Yingsha\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13382519\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sun_Yingsha\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sun_Yingsha\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The report\", \"from\": 944, \"to\": 954}, {\"ngram\": \"the pair\", \"from\": 973, \"to\": 981}, {\"ngram\": \"the world number\", \"from\